# https://docs.amplify.aws/cli/teams/shared#sharing-projects-within-the-team
# "If you want to share a project publicly and open source your serverless infrastructure, you should remove or put the amplify/team-provider-info.json file in the .gitignore file."
**/amplify/team-provider-info.json

# Auto-generated by amplify, but with `**` added to cover all environments
**/amplify/
**/src/
**/build/
**/dist/
**/node_modules/
**/aws-exports.js
**/awsconfiguration*
**/amplify_outputs*
**/amplifyconfiguration*
**/amplify-build-config.json
**/amplify-gradle-config.json
**/amplifytools.xcconfig
**/.secret-*
**/.amplify/
**/.vscode/
**/.gitignore

# Keep previously-committed AI amplify due to specific example app requirements
!environments/ai/*/amplify/*/*/resource*
!environments/ai/*/amplify/backend*
